nodes.text: Cagaran Wei was a male scientist and doctor who lived in Hweg Shul, the capital city of Nam Chorios. For twenty years, he was married to a woman jeweler who died in a landspeeder accident. A Latecomer, Doctor Wei disappeared inexplicably in 44 ABY without a trace. Later he was found dead at site of Rock ivory processing plant by exiled Grand Master Luke Skywalker, Jedi Knight Ben Skywalker and Sith apprentice Vestara Khai.
